{"tid":1173241,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"突然諗返起中學早會嗰陣，學校個神父講過自己以前幫人驅過魔","createTime":"2019-05-27T03:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T06:54:00.000Z","uid":154872,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9f9bd6a1f09a10a66188508804e9992d96507bb8","tid":1173241,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T03:33:51.000Z","msg":"學校係天主教中學<br />\n<br />\n記得嗰陣我中六，<br />\n<br />\n臨近Halloween, 個神父早會嗰陣開咪語重心長地叫我地唔好去玩鬼屋啊，或者扮鬼<br />\n<br />\n佢話佢以前有年青人玩呢啲或者碟仙，而搞到奶野<br />\n<br />\n然後要佢去驅魔，嗰陣早會全中學啲老師同學生都呆撚晒<br />\n<br />\n個神父而家已經不在人世，但同佢傾過計同根據其他老師/神職人員講<br />\n<br />\n佢真係去過梵諦岡到上驅魔班，亦都真係幫過人驅魔<br />\n<br />\n其他有咩想知可以再問<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇手足學校都有類似野爆"},{"pid":"f6851fd57a84a5e29011d5502317152f8308a7e9","tid":1173241,"uid":71579,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T03:35:54.000Z","msg":"碟仙都係佢嗰範？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc4a47025ebda5867bf7909183fd409b4520430","tid":1173241,"uid":243093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T03:36:10.000Z","msg":"牙占有沒見過鬼 (紅魔鬼唔計)"},{"pid":"3f2b801188b5ab48d93372bdea92c28636502273","tid":1173241,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T03:36:53.000Z","msg":"其實啲人話未見過唔信 其實係一種幸福 活係神父嘅世界佢想唔信都唔得"},{"pid":"000079048b691e2eac4fbb451397bc559261cc58","tid":1173241,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T03:37:59.000Z","msg":"灑聖水"},{"pid":"a5605537cda20d77c7c3a56dc4af45683d3b6079","tid":1173241,"uid":154872,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6851fd57a84a5e29011d5502317152f8308a7e9","tid":1173241,"uid":71579,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T03:35:54.000Z","msg":"碟仙都係佢嗰範？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T03:38:08.000Z","msg":"唔知<br />\n<br />\n佢咁講，我照覆述，<br />\n<br />\n後尾同神父本人傾開，佢話嗰次係成功的"},{"pid":"bf34